Dear T3E Users,

SGI/Cray Research is offering a t-shirt to anyone who completely answers the
questionnaire below.  This is not a NERSC survey.  If you wish to give your
input to SGI/Cray please respond directly to Steve Caruso, caruso@cray.com.

